high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk to the fridge that's in the corner to your right and stand in front of it facing it.
Chill the in the lettuce fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the lettuce on the table near the corner under the salt.

Pick up the lettuce from the table
Turn left and go as far as the stove then turn right and go to the wall then turn left and head to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge to chill then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn left and then turn left and go to the garbage bag in the corner then turn right to face the table
Put the lettuce in front of the spoon on the table

high_descs: Go to the wall on your left, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the table.
Go around the table clockwise to the wall, then go left to the refrigerator.
Refrigerate the lettuce, then remove it from the fridge.
Face the opposite direction to go between the wall and the left end of the table, then turn right to face the end of the table.
Put the lettuce in front of the spoon that is near you on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on a kitchen table.
